@Pyrra.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7294

### Cadastrar um usu·rio novo
POST {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste2@pyrra.com",
  "password": "senha12345",
  "name": "Vitor"
}

### Fazer login
POST {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@pyrra.com",
  "password": "senha12345"
}

### Acessar rota protegida (troque TOKEN_AQUI pelo token retornado no login)
GET {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

### Criar um foco (deve virar Exercicio, peso alto)
POST {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

{
  "name": "treinar na academia"
}

### Criar outro foco (deve virar Hidratacao, peso baixo)
POST {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

{
  "name": "beber agua"
}

### Listar meus focos
GET {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos
Authorization: BearereyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

### Ver a pontuaÁ„o do dia (antes de qualquer check-in novo)
GET {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos/score
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

### Fazer check-in do foco "beber agua" (peso 5)
POST {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos/61fc8cac-16c0-4682-9076-ef1245603fc6/checkin
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

### Fazer check-in do foco "treinar na academia" (peso 20)
POST {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos/9a925253-012c-4983-ac61-30d0977f7329/checkin
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

### Ver a pontuaÁ„o do dia (depois dos dois check-ins)
GET {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos/score
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

### Desativar foco duplicado (beber agua extra)
DELETE {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos/3226e418-c53a-4656-a29d-361c6d2d3bee
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

### Desativar foco duplicado (treinar extra)
DELETE {{Pyrra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/focos/b55ea7f8-2dd6-4300-9e8b-6ffbeeeecb83
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..oINlGgX0Txd9oNald5NqVd5ObwB-aYAKOkd64Kprrds

